Services

Service Actions

  • AddHttpProxyRule
  • GetHttpProxyParameters
  • RemoveHttpProxyRule

HttpProxy2

http://linksys.com/jnap/httpproxy/HttpProxy2
This service provides managing http proxy rules on the router.

Service Actions

  • AddHttpProxyRule
  • GetHttpProxyParameters
  • RemoveHttpProxyRule

Actions

AddHttpProxyRule

http://linksys.com/jnap/httpproxy/AddHttpProxyRule
This action adds a new HTTP Proxy rule.

Note:

This action is safe to call within the context of a transaction.

Input Parameters

Name Type Optional Description
headerToken string yes Http header token.
passPhrase string yes Pass phrase for URL encryption.
useSSL bool no Use SSL for encryption or not.
acls HttpACL[] no An array of access control list.
sessionUUID UUID yes Session UUID associated with the http proxy rule

Output Parameters

Name Type Optional Description
ruleUUID UUID no rule UUID identifies a rule.

Result

http://linksys.com/jnap/httpproxy/AddHttpProxyRuleResult
Value Description
OK Success.
Error
ErrorInvalidACLType The ACLType could only be Allow or Deny.
ErrorInvalidDestPort The port should be between 0 and 65535.
ErrorInvalidIpv4PrefixLength The ipv4PrefixLength should be at the range of [0, 32].
ErrorInvalidIpv6PrefixLength The ipv6PrefixLength should be at the range of [0, 64].
ErrorSessionDoesNotExist The specified session does not exit.
ErrorTooManyAclsPerHttpProxyRule MAX is 10.
ErrorTooManyHttpProxyRules MAX is 20.
_ErrorAbortedAction
_ErrorInvalidInput
_ErrorInvalidOutput
_ErrorNotReady
_ErrorSessionVerification
_ErrorUnauthorized
_ErrorUnexpected
_ErrorUnknownAction
_ErrorUnknownSession

Sample Transaction

POST [request-uri] HTTP/1.1
Host: 192.168.1.1
Content-Type: application/json; charset=utf-8
Content-Length: [number of octets in request body]
X-JNAP-Action: "http://linksys.com/jnap/httpproxy/AddHttpProxyRule"

{
  "headerToken": "DA8289C90A70434CA971270052518AFBABE443E51D7C422E9143192C9723E0FB",
  "passPhrase": "Hi, this a a pass phrase!",
  "useSSL": true,
  "acls": [
    {
      "aclType": "Allow",
      "ipv4Address": "172.10.23.136",
      "ipv4PrefixLength": 8,
      "ipv6Address": "FE80:0000:0000:0000:20D0:58FF:FE73:4CF1",
      "ipv6PrefixLength": 16,
      "destPort": 9999
    }
  ],
  "sessionUUID": "03d2bd9f-015d-4a7b-92ac-0c17ef5b4548"
}
HTTP/1.1 200 OK
Content-Type: application/json; charset=utf-8
Content-Length: [number of octets in response body]

{
  "result": "OK",
  "output": {
    "ruleUUID": "7e04d3bb-8789-4d6b-b8d1-d9b070dfe24e"
  }
}

GetHttpProxyParameters

http://linksys.com/jnap/httpproxy/GetHttpProxyParameters
This action gets http proxy parameters.

Note:

This action is safe to call within the context of a transaction.

Input Parameters

This action does not have any input parameters.

Output Parameters

Name Type Optional Description
httpPort int no Http port
httpsPort int no Https port
maxHttpProxyRules int no Max number of http proxy rules allowed on the router
maxACLRulesPerHttpProxyRule int no Max number of ACL rules per http proxy rule allowed on the router

Result

http://linksys.com/jnap/httpproxy/GetHttpProxyParametersResult
Value Description
OK Success.
Error
_ErrorAbortedAction
_ErrorInvalidInput
_ErrorInvalidOutput
_ErrorNotReady
_ErrorSessionVerification
_ErrorUnauthorized
_ErrorUnexpected
_ErrorUnknownAction
_ErrorUnknownSession

Sample Transaction

POST [request-uri] HTTP/1.1
Host: 192.168.1.1
Content-Type: application/json; charset=utf-8
Content-Length: [number of octets in request body]
X-JNAP-Action: "http://linksys.com/jnap/httpproxy/GetHttpProxyParameters"

{
}
HTTP/1.1 200 OK
Content-Type: application/json; charset=utf-8
Content-Length: [number of octets in response body]

{
  "result": "OK",
  "output": {
    "httpPort": 80,
    "httpsPort": 8080,
    "maxHttpProxyRules": 20,
    "maxACLRulesPerHttpProxyRule": 5
  }
}

RemoveHttpProxyRule

http://linksys.com/jnap/httpproxy/RemoveHttpProxyRule
This action removes HTTP Proxy rule.

Note:

This action is safe to call within the context of a transaction.

Input Parameters

Name Type Optional Description
ruleUUID UUID no Rule UUID identifies a rule.

Output Parameters

This action does not have any output parameters.

Result

http://linksys.com/jnap/httpproxy/RemoveHttpProxyRuleResult
Value Description
OK Success.
Error
ErrorHttpProxyRuleDoesNotExist The rule does not exist.
_ErrorAbortedAction
_ErrorInvalidInput
_ErrorInvalidOutput
_ErrorNotReady
_ErrorSessionVerification
_ErrorUnauthorized
_ErrorUnexpected
_ErrorUnknownAction
_ErrorUnknownSession

Structures

HttpACL

http://linksys.com/jnap/httpproxy/HttpACL
A HttpACL rule describing an entry of IP access control lists for lighttpd

Structure Members

Member Name Type Optional Description
aclType ACLType no ACL type.
ipv4Address IPAddress yes Source IPv4 address
ipv4PrefixLength int yes The IPv4 prefix length. This value must be between 0 and 32.
ipv6Address IPv6Address yes Source IPv6 address
ipv6PrefixLength int yes The IPv6 prefix length. This value must be between 0 and 64.
destPort int yes Destination port of rule

Enumerations

ACLType

http://linksys.com/jnap/httpproxy/ACLType
ACL type.

Enumeration Values

Value Description
Allow Allow.
Deny Deny.
